      build --release` before `dpkg-buildpackage`. debian/rules
      already wiped target/ via override_dh_auto_clean and rebuilt
      via override_dh_auto_build, so the pre-build was pure
      duplicated work (~60s per pipeline). dpkg-buildpackage now
      drives the release build end to end.
