pam-certauth (0.3.15-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * fly-dm greeter: surface PAM_TEXT_INFO on the lock screen.
    pam_certauth sends "Это устройство: host_id=..." and the
    p12_wrong_pin_diagnostic via io.show_info(), but fly-dm only
    forwards info-messages to the greeter UI when
    `greeter-show-messages = true` is set under `[greeter]` in
