        fly-dmrc.bak.<UTC>, preserves attrs. Flags
        --enable-greeter-messages (default ON for fly-dm*) and
        --no-greeter-messages (CI / non-interactive deploys).
        --unintegrate does NOT touch fly-dmrc.
      - New startup-check module `fly_dm_greeter` reads fly-dmrc
        and emits an Info record on every daemon start / `check`
        run: fly_dm_greeter_messages_on / _off / _default /
        _read_failed. Silent skip when the file is absent
        (sshd-only hosts, server stands). Wired into
        run_startup_checks and re-exported as check_fly_dm_greeter.

